00:06:45,577 --> 00:06:47,618
dropped before it slips into the lava, as it were.

109
00:06:49,860 --> 00:06:50,261
Some games...

110
00:06:51,412 --> 00:06:54,834
give the player a mechanic for managing the cost of their own potential failure

111
00:06:55,254 --> 00:06:58,576
while still staying within the kind of narrative logic of the game, or the metaphor of the game,

