00:09:34,206 --> 00:09:35,787
So guess what? You're going to have to deal with that.

155
00:09:40,785 --> 00:09:45,346
That's why we would like to look at how to bring that player mitigation back into the

156
00:09:45,426 --> 00:09:47,727
fold of the core game experience.

157
00:09:48,628 --> 00:09:54,370
We want to expose the player to survivable changes in their immediate situation from

158
00:09:54,390 --> 00:09:57,511
which they can then find their way back to something stronger, something more sustainable.

159
00:10:01,293 --> 00:10:04,774
So think about why a player spins out in the middle of a race.

