00:10:06,057 --> 00:10:08,480
it's because they're doing the thing they're supposed to be doing

161
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:12,223
they're driving fast, they're driving as fast as they possibly can, they're driving

162
00:10:12,283 --> 00:10:12,844
too fast

