00:13:04,357 --> 00:13:08,879
fault tolerance. And in describing the player's experience on Far Cry 2 for example which

208
00:13:08,919 --> 00:13:15,602
was this kind of friction generated by systems like malaria, Max is laughing at me, weapons

209
00:13:15,682 --> 00:13:21,084
jamming, fire, propagating fire, all these various other functions, the player is really

210
00:13:21,905 --> 00:13:23,866
getting hit with these kind of small inputs.

211
00:13:24,467 --> 00:13:26,468
And they rarely die from these events,

212
00:13:27,229 --> 00:13:28,830
but it's unpredictable, right?

