00:13:59,422 --> 00:14:02,144
And you need to somehow get the thing down without loss of

228
00:14:02,204 --> 00:14:02,765
craft or crew.

229
00:14:02,785 --> 00:14:05,346
OK, well, that's cute.

230
00:14:05,627 --> 00:14:07,488
But we need a more formal definition than that.

